model.factories

Class EntityFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.factories.EntityFactory

  • public class EntityFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity factory which abstracts the creation of an entity. It loads the entity map for a given terrain or randomly generates entities for testing.

    This is probably the ugliest class I have ever written.

    Author:
    Marcel van Workum - 300313949, Reuben Puketapu - 300310939
